[[include :scp-wiki:info:start]]
**SCP-CN-2304** The Sun Is Tired of Rising
**Author:** [[*user DouglasLiu]], author page **[http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/douglasliu-author-page here]**
**Translated by:** [[*user tetsusquared]]
[[collapsible show="▼ Author's Note" hide="▲ Author's Note"]]
The use of pure gold and some of these numbers aren't quite as arbitrary as you think.
[[/collapsible]]
[[include :scp-wiki:info:end]]

[[div class="myImageBlock" style="width: 30%; float: right; margin: 1em 0 1em 1em"]]
[[div class="sunImage"]]
☉
[[/div]]
[[div class="myImageCaption"]]
**Symbol-2304**
[[/div]]
[[/div]]

**Item #:** SCP-CN-2304

**Object Class:** Thaumiel

**Special Containment Procedures:** Each regional department is to select one site in each country to be responsible for performing SCP-CN-2304. The site is to maintain sufficient personnel on hand to perform SCP-CN-2304 between 00:00 and 04:00 local time every day. In order to mitigate the damage caused by repeated execution of SCP-CN-2304 by personnel, it is recommended that each site rotate personnel according to the situation. 

If the normal rising of SCP-CN-2304-1 is not observed following the execution of SCP-CN-2304, the site must immediately inform the Overseer Council and all sites are to be on guard for a possible veil disruption scenario emergency.

**Description:** SCP-CN-2304 is an anomalous ritual, developed and confirmed to be effective by the applied theology department of Site-CN-44 of the Foundation's Chinese branch. The complete steps required to perform SCP-CN-2304 are: 

# No less than 33 people are to gather around an empty area, with no more than 1.5m between each person and the nearest other person.
# Each person is to hold 2 g of pure gold in their mouth and kneel down facing east.
# Each person uses a sharp implement made of solid gold to make a wound and draw blood (it is recommended to cut a fingertip) and draw Symbol-2304 with the resulting blood at a suitable distance in front of them.
# Each person holds their forehead to the drawn ritual pattern and holds the position for 30 minutes. The ceremony is then to be declared complete.

SCP-CN-2304-1 is the sun following 23/04/2021. Without intervention, the natural rising of SCP-CN-2304-1 from the east cannot be detected from any location on Earth, and the presence of SCP-CN-2304-1 cannot be sensed from any location in the Earth's atmosphere. As of now, the daily use of SCP-CN-2304 is the only way to prevent the above-mentioned anomaly.

